00:00:23,058 --> 00:00:28,862
10 things that while we were developing Hearthstone we found to be very very useful

6
00:00:28,902 --> 00:00:32,404
sort of as high-level design things so I'm going to talk a little bit about the specifics

7
00:00:33,104 --> 00:00:36,126
of the things we did and also sort of why those things are important.

8
00:00:36,926 --> 00:00:40,347
And so here are the things that I'm going to be talking about.

