00:16:26,492 --> 00:16:29,373
have summoning sickness in there it just makes for a much worse game to not have

221
00:16:29,413 --> 00:16:32,835
summoning sickness so this is an example of something where we tried to simplify

222
00:16:33,635 --> 00:16:37,297
the depth was just not there after we simplified so we just decided we're

