00:16:52,938 --> 00:16:54,920
And so when we're talking about the game, we're going,

227
00:16:54,940 --> 00:16:58,263
okay, this is sort of the right level of simplicity that we want.

228
00:16:58,863 --> 00:16:59,124
And then...

229
00:17:00,665 --> 00:17:07,654
over time we start adding additional things to the game here and there for various reasons and and often it's like a little thing here

