00:18:30,476 --> 00:18:32,477
much more complicated than I would have liked.

245
00:18:32,837 --> 00:18:34,438
So that's certainly an area that, you know,

246
00:18:34,498 --> 00:18:35,659
if I could travel back in time,

247
00:18:35,699 --> 00:18:37,440
I would have gone back and seen what we could have done

248
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:40,042
to make it more simpler or more integrated

249
00:18:40,082 --> 00:18:40,803
or something like that.

250
00:18:41,043 --> 00:18:43,404
But it's an example where you just never stop adding stuff,

251
00:18:44,045 --> 00:18:44,825
or certainly we don't.

252
00:18:48,293 --> 00:18:56,359
So the next big point is sort of a super obvious one, keep it deep, and it's sort of of course at odds with the simplify idea.

253
00:18:56,959 --> 00:19:06,526
