254
00:19:07,358 --> 00:19:15,282
And if we ever remove complexity and also remove depth, we thought about that change like the summoning sickness one.

255
00:19:16,223 --> 00:19:24,007
Or if we ever were in a case where we felt like we really had to simplify the game and we were going to lose some depth,

256
00:19:24,307 --> 00:19:30,171
we then thought about what's an idea that we can put back into the game to make sure that we still have all of that depth there

257
00:19:30,831 --> 00:19:32,812
that's not as complex as the previous idea.

258
00:19:33,613 --> 00:19:40,681
So probably the biggest biggest thing that we did in Hearthstone to sort of address that directly was hero powers

259
00:19:41,982 --> 00:19:42,102
and

260
00:19:43,696 --> 00:19:45,456
In some other collectible card games

261
00:19:45,496 --> 00:19:51,178
There's a variety of things that you can do with your mana on the board and you can play cards out of your hand and other

262
00:19:51,218 --> 00:19:54,319
Things so there's a lot of combinatorics and as we change the game

