00:21:42,089 --> 00:21:46,230
Figure out what it meant. So if I have to I'm reading along and I go what was that word?

284
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:51,792
Oh, yeah, that word means this other thing. Okay, I had to stop and it's a bit of a jarring experience and we really want

