00:24:16,397 --> 00:24:19,438
Another thing that was pretty important, and I think it's pretty straightforward,

316
00:24:19,478 --> 00:24:23,560
but that as long as the player has learned enough to actually start playing

317
00:24:23,600 --> 00:24:27,903
the real game, we didn't want to teach them anything else. So sort of our goal

