00:30:04,015 --> 00:30:07,738
So another thing that was important to us, and it's kind of funny to be saying this,

400
00:30:07,758 --> 00:30:11,061
because on one hand I'm saying we wanted to look at what we wanted to be changing,

401
00:30:11,101 --> 00:30:13,082
and on the other hand I'm saying don't change too much.

402
00:30:13,823 --> 00:30:18,326
And what I mean really by don't change too much is make sure that all of the

403
00:30:18,366 --> 00:30:21,308
things that players are sort of expecting when they come to your game,

